{
  "stem": "10905.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was-- since I was born in September-- anybody that was born after September 1st didn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to be-- you have to be six by September 1.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So even later on when we lived in Budapest, I did not have to go to school because I was born September 20th, and I had to wait for the following year, which would have been September of '44.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we did everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we-- we enjoyed a very nice life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We lived with my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After I learned how to speak Hungarian, we lived with my-- with my grandma at her house-- my mother's mother, the Goldner house.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my other grandmother, my father's mother, lived in town as well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we visited with her, and we attended all the holidays, went to synagogue and played.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to go to cemetery on Sundays sometimes and did everything as if-- to me, I didn't-- I was not aware that there was a war going on or any problems going on.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One day, my parents-- then, things changed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They sent a German officer with his Shepherd to stay with us-- not with us, but to stay-- you know, you had to house them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to house them in my grandmother's house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- he was billeted there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was billeted there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had to have been a nice person.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, he was not mean or nasty to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, he came, and he went and never bothered us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You remember?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was not afraid, because you know, he had a nice, nice, nice dog.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He kept to his room.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
